creator: Pixel Art Book Color By Number - Pop It 3D Games
descriptionHtml:
If you are a beauty conscious & makeup lover who wants to organize the messy cosmetic drawers, then you are absolutely at the right place. Try this restock game. This DIY game is for you to organize your Vanity drawers according to your own choice. This is one of the best Antistress games with soothing ASMR effects.
When it’s about organizational skills no one compromises on this. Everyone wants a disciplined and organized room and tidy stuff. Either it’s about “Organized Room, Tidy Closet, Fill the fridge or sort the makeup you can all do it yourself.
The purpose to design this game is when you get back to home sweet home after spending a huge amount on purchase of cosmetics. The 1st thing comes into your mind is to keep the makeup in sorted & assembled form so you can feel relaxed & calm down.
Start restocking drawers with different cosmetics stuff like foundation, Lipstick, cream & many more.

How To Play:
- Tap to open the drawer in a cozy puzzle game and say goodbye to cluttered beauty items and hello to a more organized makeup kit.
- Tap & Drop fashion items in an arranged form just like a beautician salon.
- Another sack would be suggested full of makeover items like lipstick, eyeliner, mascara, bronzer & other stuff to sort n fit.
- You are supposed to empty the sack and adjust cosmetics by dragging a little to left in a limited space.
- Just drag & drop items in the kit box and move to the next level to fill the makeup organizer.
- With our fashion makeover planner, you'll never have to spend time wondering what to do in the morning. Our makeover studio is your go-to source for styling inspiration.
- With Restock Fill the Makeup box, you'll be able to make the most of your kit space and essentials. Never overbuy beauty makeup items again, and save time by streamlining your makeover wardrobe with makeup sort organize game.

Features:
- Various levels with different challenges of 3d makeup organizer.
- Challenging levels of makeup sorting, filling & makeover kit organization.
- Drag-and-drop or similar mechanics to sort the beauty items.
- FREE to enjoy the sort puzzle game with wonderful makeover storage.
- Satisfying refill feeling with ASMR experience
- Organizing games with only one finger control.
- Best time killer game with time limits or other challenges that make the sorting task more difficult.
- Power-ups and bonuses that can help beauticians sort makeups more quickly or earn bonus points.
- A variety of difficulty levels to keep the makeup app challenging and engaging.

This makeup organizing game will help you to explore your artistic as well as organizational skills. Let’s boost your energy by playing this interesting game & be an organized beauty product creator. Have a luxurious & beautiful lifestyle with this beauty makeup game.
